<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><id>https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=110&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0</id><title>HKDiscuss house</title><updated>2025-07-05T03:08:53.093517+00:00</updated><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=110&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0"/><generator uri="https://lkiesow.github.io/python-feedgen" version="1.0.0">python-feedgen</generator><subtitle>Latest articles</subtitle><entry><id>a8ac60d22e44bb97eafcda8b86d1797d</id><title>🆘創新低價｜青衣灝景灣2房666萬沽  造價同類近年低</title><updated>2025-07-04T10:48:07+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-04T10:48:07+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573098585"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573098585"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F3974031%2F%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25BD%258E%25E5%2583%25B9%25EF%25BD%259C%25E9%259D%2592%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E7%2581%259D%25E6%2599%25AF%25E7%2581%25A32%25E6%2588%25BF666%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%25B2%25BD%25C2%25A0%2520%25E9%2580%25A0%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%2590%258C%25E9%25A1%259E%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BD%258E%3Fmtc%3D60037&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=ce90ec88e4b776bd1268eb704eb47cde&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://ps.hket.com/article/3974 ...  造價同類近年低?mtc=60037&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;私樓成交&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;撰文：陳嘉敏&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;發布時間：10分鐘前&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;市場消息指，青衣灝景灣2房以新低價易手。成交為灝景灣1座中層D室，實用面積537呎，成交價666萬元，實用呎價12402元，造價為同類單位近年低價。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原業主於2011年以396萬入市，今轉手帳面獲利270萬。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;據土地註冊處資料，灝景灣最新成交為10座高層A室室，實用面積789平方呎，成交價1220萬，實用呎價15463元。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31973320&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=10236047256868974537fb77_03773391"/><published>2025-07-04T10:48:07+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>a0b07441ca3c2c71150645792494c9dc</id><title>結業潮｜尖沙咀火鍋店「漁一」結業 店家自爆生意慘淡 周日生意曾僅得$2000</title><updated>2025-07-04T10:48:14+08:00</updated><author><name>931931</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-04T10:48:14+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573098587"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573098587"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="58" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_47.gif"&gt;遊客區都2000一日... 經濟好到不得了.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;【結業潮2025/執笠/開業/新舖】結業聲音不斷，位於尖沙咀中港城平台的火鍋店「漁一海鮮火鍋料理」，早前亦突然宣布停業，並引用電影《破地獄》金句「人一出生就倒數」，稱「漁一到咗站都係要落車」。&lt;br/&gt;店主又在留言中提到，店舖生意慘淡，經營得十分吃力，「之前星期日，可以全日得$2000生意，所以唔想浪費電力所以（父親節）無開」&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://ps.hket.com/article/3973665/%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD%E6%BD%AE%EF%BD%9C%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%92%80%E7%81%AB%E9%8D%8B%E5%BA%97%E3%80%8C%E6%BC%81%E4%B8%80%E3%80%8D%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD%E3%80%80%E5%BA%97%E5%AE%B6%E8%87%AA%E7%88%86%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F%E6%85%98%E6%B7%A1%E3%80%80%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F%E6%9B%BE%E5%83%85%E5%BE%97-2000?mtc=60037" target="_blank" uhash="52a7a885fa82da199bb666bba3238d0e"&gt;結業潮｜尖沙咀火鍋店「漁一」結業店家自爆生意慘淡周日生意曾僅得$2000&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31973321&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=10236047256868974537fb77_03773391"/><published>2025-07-04T10:48:14+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>b581d435a9a286592a3a7bf73858120f</id><title>如果發展商爆煲，未賣出嘅樓點算</title><updated>2025-07-04T11:02:51+08:00</updated><author><name>炒家</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-04T11:02:51+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573098762"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573098762"&gt;清咗盤，會唔會變咗鬼城&lt;br&gt;買咗班友會唔會孤零零一個&lt;br/&gt;會唔會有回音喺走廊&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31973329&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=10236047256868974537fb77_03773391"/><published>2025-07-04T11:02:51+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>c302d165a6aeb625ef46cbe94fe5db43</id><title>蝕讓成交｜沙田第一城2房419萬沽 7年蝕近170萬離場</title><updated>2025-07-04T13:03:43+08:00</updated><author><name>931931</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-04T13:03:43+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573099962"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573099962"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="58" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_47.gif"&gt;AA又成功開單啦... 沙一真系易開單&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;中原地產副區域營業董事吳焯誠表示，沙田第一城7月至今短短4天錄7宗成交，最新包括29座中層C室，實用面積327平方呎，2房間隔，原本叫價約428萬元，議價後以419萬元易手，呎價12,813元。&lt;br/&gt;據了解，新買家為上車客，見近期樓市氣氛轉好，加上單位價錢合理，即入市單位自住。原業主於2018年以約588萬元購入單位，持貨約7年，是次轉手帳面蝕約169萬元離場，期內貶值約28.7%。&lt;br/&gt;土地註冊處資料顯示，沙田第一城對上成交為52座中層G室，實用面積303平方呎，上月底以395萬元沽出，呎價13,036元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://ps.hket.com/article/3974060/%E8%9D%95%E8%AE%93%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4%EF%BD%9C%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%9F%8E2%E6%88%BF419%E8%90%AC%E6%B2%BD%207%E5%B9%B4%E8%9D%95%E8%BF%91170%E8%90%AC%E9%9B%A2%E5%A0%B4?mtc=60037" target="_blank" uhash="341bf4a931a01791853a7db131efd8d0"&gt;蝕讓成交｜沙田第一城2房419萬沽 7年蝕近170萬離場&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31973384&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=10236047256868974537fb77_03773391"/><published>2025-07-04T13:03:43+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>c2f0fde997855e23f83e413df503e099</id><title>窮淡老豆老母都幾自私</title><updated>2025-07-04T13:35:11+08:00</updated><author><name>P-back</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-04T13:35:11+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573100371"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573100371"&gt;自己冇樓捱窮都仲未夠， 仲要生下一代出嚟受，以為可以幫自己脫離苦困 點知又係一堆廢物&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;[&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt; 本帖最後由 P-back 於 2025-7-4 17:57 編輯 &lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31973403&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=10236047256868974537fb77_03773391"/><published>2025-07-04T13:35:11+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>979a34d846564758610c8f65cf15b113</id><title>〖牛氣沖天〗🔥🔥🔥 火炭星凱·堤岸3房逾1983萬沽 項目分層單位🔥🔥🔥全數沽清🔥🔥🔥</title><updated>2025-07-04T14:08:22+08:00</updated><author><name>stoddort</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-04T14:08:22+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573100703"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573100703"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #0000ff; "&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;最近個市，的確好旺，貨尾都賣清！！！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573100703" original-img="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3970000/3974135/lkta20230213001_2500x2500_1_1024.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3970000/3974135/lkta20230213001_2500x2500_1_1024.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/36f51a/f/800x0/https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3970000/3974135/lkta20230213001_2500x2500_1_1024.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;▲星凱·堤岸&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;有半新盤再錄成交，中洲置業營銷策劃總監楊聰永指出，火炭星凱‧堤岸今日（4日）再售出1伙3房戶，單位為3座49樓C室，其實用面積945平方呎，成交價1983.4萬元，呎價約20,988元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;他補充，項目所有分層單位已經沽清，僅餘下最後5間特色單位。項目開售至今累售1,330伙，佔全盤1,335逾99%。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #0000ff; "&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;樓價同租金又爆升&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573100703" original-img="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/foshantou/fst_scare.gif" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/foshantou/fst_scare.gif" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/6da5d5/f/800x0/https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/foshantou/fst_scare.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;班窮酸淡可以７街瞓&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573100703" original-img="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/foshantou/fst_scare.gif" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/foshantou/fst_scare.gif" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/6da5d5/f/800x0/https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/foshantou/fst_scare.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=3434944" target="_blank"&gt;@~kurapika~&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=7321592" target="_blank"&gt;@過去深愛的羊腩&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=7333091" target="_blank"&gt;@vovovo.N&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=7256576" target="_blank"&gt;@叔叔要不要&lt;/a&gt;分身Account&lt;a class="usertag" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=3395993" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span uid="3395993"&gt;@Youngbro&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&l