0dd3bf297c04a24oLbBdHNj86ui.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16337574_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"/&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16337574&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IMG_20250628_074628.jpg_1751320725509.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (594.85 KB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-7-1 06:04&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;訂埋早一晚的酒店，一到立即check in補眠2小時&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;[&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt; 本帖最後由 stevenchoi 於 2025-7-3 07:38 編輯 &lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31970570&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=110&amp;utm_campaign=1076&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-07-01T06:04:24+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>5a49dc344b4d37a8ca2ccdb2b257dd89</id><title>北京蘭州北京11天, 好長氣的遊記</title><updated>2025-07-03T09:18:46+08:00</updated><author><name>kc60wong</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-03T09:18:46+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573084505"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573084505"&gt;第1天,6月11星期三&lt;br&gt;6月11出發,2人行,乘11.20西九高鐵,一等坐,人仔1997/人, 19.30到北京西站。&lt;br/&gt;近年好少出門,一年只上過幾次深圳。第一次坐高鐵,很興奮。&lt;br/&gt;當日早上10.00去站內添好運食D野,亦已在車上點了外賣。&lt;br/&gt;10.30食完,站內行下睇下, 11.00入閘安檢過關,11.10上車。&lt;br/&gt;原來車門會在開車前5min關閉。準時開車。&lt;br/&gt;個踏腳板安裝在前面坐位,於是後面位仁姐細細力伸一下腳,你就小震一下。&lt;br/&gt;在深圳北送上了KFC葡撻,廣州南送上了水蛋排骨飯, D野都OK好食。&lt;br/&gt;車上服務員送上免費飲品,小吃,似坐飛機。&lt;br/&gt;車上用alipay買了杯咖啡,poor。可能訊號弱,想網上定野比錢,好多失敗&lt;br/&gt;想定故宮門票,原來要好多日預定,最後在trip.com&lt;br/&gt;定了6月19,有領隊,有填鴨餐的票,約250/人。&lt;br/&gt;又定了13日恭王府門票, 20元/人。&lt;br/&gt;7.30準時到北京西。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31972442&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=110&amp;utm_campaign=1076&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-07-03T09:18:46+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>015c5e7d28d448ddca33d4009eecf2c9</id><title>高明錦鯉文化園</title><updated>2025-07-01T16:28:24+08:00</updated><author><name>timmywu</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-01T16:28:24+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573063156"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573063156"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16338641" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573063156" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250701/20250701_14fa0f6eaa1a9029e41bHBA6zrrc43Mz.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/46764e/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250701/20250701_14fa0f6eaa1a9029e41bHBA6zrrc43Mz.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16338641_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16338641&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;20250630_150830.jpg_1751358498598.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (460.18 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-7-1 16:28&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;span id="attach_16338642" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573063156" original-im